From Henry Spencer Subject Re Lunar Colony Race By or In article Matthew Feulner writes Need to find atleast for prize My first thought is Ross After further consideration I think he'd be more likely to try to win come in a disappointing Try Bill Try Sam Walton's When the Lunar Society's estimate of the cost of a lunar colony was mentioned at Making Orbit somebody asked Jerry Pournelle have you talked to Bill Gates The answer He says that if he were going to sink that much money into it he'd want to run it and he doesn't have the Somebody then asked him about Answer Having Ross Perot on your board may be a bigger problem than not having the All work is one man's Henry Spencer U of Toronto Zoology Kipling utzoo henry